Description: QR Code Link to This Post   Looking for a decent mid range phone that won't set you back too much?  This is a good phone.  I have the S21 Ultra and the S10 Lite by comparison is not bad at all.  Sure it doesn't have all the crazy camera features of the S21 Ultra, but it has a very decent camera (48-megapixel (f/2.0) + 12-megapixel (f/2.2) + 5-megapixel (f/2.4), screen is big and bright (just a tiny bit smaller than S21 Ultra), graphics, gaming and smoothness of scrolling nothing to complain about, and its internet connectivity with a decent provider is excellent.  And this thing has something the S21 Ultra doesn't.  That's right!  A micro SD port!  And did I mention it's like in mint condition because it's hardly been used?  It's like new as it was always kept in fully armored case (which is included) the short period it was used.
